do the valuation you requested?

437
00:44:58,320 --> 00:44:59,116
Get away.

438
00:45:00,280 --> 00:45:03,078
Get away from my car!

439
00:45:04,680 --> 00:45:06,318
Get away from my car!

440
00:45:10,840 --> 00:45:14,753
The car is next, fine!
