458
00:46:34,560 --> 00:46:36,437
I'll tell you what we're going to do.

459
00:46:37,480 --> 00:46:38,993
We're going to roll with the dice.

460
00:46:41,040 --> 00:46:42,951
Now, if it lands on a 1, 2, or 3,

461
00:46:43,800 --> 00:46:45,916
